<title>JESUS IS OUR PROTECTOR</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I kikhen u khah Lal Isu'n ei vengin,
 Tuhin hing le-damin I kimuu hi;
 Kipak tak leh lungguol in kikhawm hitiu,
 Thawmhaute chuh nuom takin um hitiu.

[V2]
 Isun dama ei, na ven gel ziekin,
 A min pakchawi an kikhawmin lasa'i tiu;
 Mihing mai kipahna chuh akim zo puoi,
 Van Thagau Thiengin ei lungmuon zing hen.

[V3]
 2. Van a Lal kawma kikhawp ding lungtup in,
 Kumsawt a go thilpha chuh muh guoi tiu;
 Pa leh mihingte muh in phat chuh guoi tiu,
 I Lal leh I suohpih a hih ziekun.

[V4]
 3. Zie khawvel ahin A na sem tadih leng,
 Van gamah aman chuh mu ding I hiu;
 Khawvel dahumna hi thuok tadih mah leng,
 A van gam nuom achun kipak nai tiu.</lyrics>
</song>